00:06:05.685 --> 00:06:13.092
Above that is the limbic area which we call as the one thousand petaled lotus.

00:06:14.427 --> 00:06:22.735
In the Bible, it is described that, "I will appear before you like tongues of flames".

00:06:22.735 --> 00:06:28.708
These tongues of flames are like petals, beautifully coloured

00:06:28.708 --> 00:06:43.256
as you see here, there are different colours to every set and they are extremely soothing to look at.

00:06:43.256 --> 00:06:51.597
They look like flames but they don’t burn. They soothe you.

00:06:52.598 --> 00:07:05.411
As it is now, we have to understand that there is a fundamental truth about yourself

00:07:06.412 --> 00:07:19.859
and that is you are not this body, this mind, this ego, these conditionings, this intelligence, emotions,

00:07:20.860 --> 00:07:24.864
but you are the Spirit.

00:07:24.864 --> 00:07:32.438
So, you have to rise to the level of selfhood as every scripture has said

00:07:33.773 --> 00:07:41.914
that you have to be born again. In Sanskrit language a Realised soul is called as "dvijaha",

00:07:42.482 --> 00:07:51.524
meaning twice born. And also, a bird is called as "dvija". Again, meaning the twice born.

00:07:51.991 --> 00:08:02.892
So, first a bird is born as an egg, a closed personality, and when it develops and matures

00:08:02.892 --> 00:08:08.572
then a bird is born out of the same egg.

00:08:08.674 --> 00:08:20.913
The same idea they have used about human beings, that first we are human beings where these two Institutions as you see are covered.

00:08:20.920 --> 00:08:31.363
But after Realisation, when the residual power of Kundalini rises and pierces through your

00:08:31.363 --> 00:08:40.405
optic chiasma which is called as Agnya Chakra then these two Institutions are sucked in

00:08:40.405 --> 00:08:48.355
and ultimately it passes through your fontanelle bone area.

00:08:48.355 --> 00:09:06.899
The second truth is that this whole cosmos is completely covered with the divine love,

00:09:06.899 --> 00:09:13.806
the Power of God’s love.

00:09:13.806 --> 00:09:23.723
We do not know about it. We are not aware of it though we have heard about it. Every scripture has described it.

00:09:23.749 --> 00:09:34.593
This All-pervading Power of God’s love is the one we have never felt, but you can see

00:09:34.593 --> 00:09:42.068
the living work, see the beautiful flowers we have here and the beautifully leaves to match them.

00:09:42.068 --> 00:09:50.913
How they have come from Mother Earth? We take everything for granted. Such beautiful things are done by nature.

00:09:50.943 --> 00:09:59.714
Even ourselves! See our heart pulsates, pulsates without we doing anything about it.

00:09:59.714 --> 00:10:08.643
Look at our eyes, they are beautiful cameras and the brain is a beautiful computer. Who has made this?

00:10:08.643 --> 00:10:17.069
Then we have evolved from amoeba to human stage. Who has done that?

00:10:17.069 --> 00:10:25.378
We do not even think. We take it for granted whatever has come to us from this All-pervading divine Power

00:10:25.378 --> 00:10:31.638
which does all the living work.

00:10:31.638 --> 00:10:39.559
This Power is the one which has evolved us to the human level.

00:10:39.559 --> 00:10:50.094
And the reflection of the same power is this Kundalini within us which has to rise like a premule in a seed.

00:10:50.094 --> 00:10:59.575
