00:19:23.424 --> 00:19:24.420
"How?"

00:19:24.420 --> 00:19:35.762
"Because when this Kundalini passes through the centre of Agnya then its sucks in the thought process".

00:19:35.762 --> 00:19:43.522
For example, the thoughts are coming either from the future or from the past.

00:19:43.522 --> 00:19:53.394
If I say, "Now you stand in your present", you cannot. We do not know the present. Either it is the future we are thinking about or we are thinking about the past.

00:19:53.394 --> 00:19:58.958
And we are jumping on the cusp of these thoughts all the time from one to another.

00:19:58.958 --> 00:20:05.885
Some people really go mad and in Switzerland, one doctor told me, "You cut my throat or do what you like but stop my thinking".

00:20:05.885 --> 00:20:11.765
So, sometimes this bombardment is too much. But when this Kundalini rises,

00:20:11.765 --> 00:20:19.129
what she does, these thoughts which rise and fall and rise and fall, there is a space in between

00:20:19.129 --> 00:20:28.336
and she stops us at that space, which is the present and is the silence.  It's the silence within us.

00:20:28.336 --> 00:20:34.040
Gradually it starts increasing and we develop that state of thoughtless awareness.

00:20:34.040 --> 00:20:50.480
When our spirituality starts growing higher than that state when the kundalini processes through your fontanelle bone area and your connection is well established.

00:20:50.480 --> 00:20:56.809
Because the Kundalini comes down, if you are sick, you have liver problem it comes down, cures you, again goes up.

00:20:56.809 --> 00:21:05.533
Then you have a problem, it goes up and down, up and down like a yo-yo and then ultimately it has to fix it itself.

00:21:05.533 --> 00:21:13.873
Once it is fixed, then you reach a state which we call as doubtless awareness, "nirvikalpa samadhi".

00:21:13.873 --> 00:21:18.963
At that state, you develop all the powers of a Realised soul.

00:21:18.963 --> 00:21:30.375
