00:21:30.375 --> 00:21:41.371
It has nothing to do with it and for that to make it reality, once you are a Realised soul

00:21:41.371 --> 00:21:49.841
automatically you understand that you are ‘that’.

00:21:49.841 --> 00:22:01.803
There is not doubt about it.  You are a Christian, you are a Muslim, you are a Hindu at the same time.

00:22:01.803 --> 00:22:06.793
Because all the essences of these religions are the same.

00:22:06.793 --> 00:22:11.009
We fight because we don’t know the absolute problem.

00:22:11.009 --> 00:22:23.810
How can all these religions be born in an absurd way that "this fights that and that fights that"?

00:22:23.810 --> 00:22:31.962
How can it be? If it is one God, if it is Divinity, how can it? Logically it cannot.

00:22:31.962 --> 00:22:38.422
So, these are all the flowers, these incarnations and prophets, who started religions.

00:22:38.422 --> 00:22:48.306
